#AZ01: According to NBC, if the ACA were repealed:
- 133M could lose protections for a pre-existing condition;
- 11M on ACA exchanges could lose insurance;
- 12M on state-based Medicaid expansion could lose coverage;
-  2M under 26 could be kicked off their parents' plan. https://t.co/OmCSoBWRZn
